---
import USLayout from '../../../../layouts/USLayout.astro';
---

<USLayout title="US Finance, Accounting & Tax Services | Ambit" description="Accounting, tax, payroll, and financial management for US businesses. US GAAP aligned, IRS compliant, and structured across federal and state requirements.">

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[88vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0F172A;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style="background-image: linear-gradient(#1E293B 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, #1E293B 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 64px 64px;"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 40%, rgba(26,68,128,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-24 lg:py-32">
      {/* <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase" style="background-color: rgba(26,68,128,0.25); border: 1px solid rgba(26,68,128,0.4); color: #93C5FD;">
          <img src="https://flagcdn.com/w20/us.png" alt="US" class="w-4 h-3 object-cover rounded-sm" />
          United States · Finance, Accounting & Tax
        </div>
      </div> */}

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black leading-[1.05] tracking-tight mb-6" style="color: #F8FAFC;">
       United States 
        <span class="block" style="color: #93C5FD;">Finance, Accounting & Tax</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mb-12 leading-relaxed" style="color: #94A3B8;">
        From growth-stage businesses to multi-state operations across the United States, Ambit structures accounting, tax, payroll, and financial management to remain consistent across IRS, federal, and state requirements.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-14">
        {['US GAAP Aligned', 'IRS Compliant', 'Federal and State Aligned', 'Sales Tax Compliant', 'Multi-State Ready'].map(label => (
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold" style="background-color: #1E293B; color: #94A3B8; border: 1px solid #334155;">{label}</span>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a href="#services" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold text-white transition-all hover:opacity-90" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a4480, #1e5ab5);">
          See Our Services
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-all hover:opacity-80" style="background-color: #1E293B; color: #94A3B8; border: 1px solid #334155;">
          Book Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== METRICS STRIP ===== -->
  <section style="background-color: #060D18; border-top: 1px solid #1E293B; border-bottom: 1px solid #1E293B;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        {[
          { metric: '500+', label: 'Clients' },
          { metric: '20+', label: 'Years',  },
          { metric: 'US GAAP', label: 'Aligned' },
          { metric: 'IRS', label: 'Compliant',  },
        ].map(({ metric, label, sub }) => (
          <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
            <div class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black mb-1" style="color: #F8FAFC;">{metric}</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1" style="color: #93C5FD;">{label}</div>
            <div class="text-xs" style="color: #475569;">{sub}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CAPABILITY MARQUEE ===== -->
  <div class="overflow-hidden py-4" style="background-color: #1a4480;">
    <div class="flex gap-12 whitespace-nowrap animate-marquee text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase" style="color: #ffffff; width: max-content;">
      {[
        'US GAAP aligned financial reporting',
        'IRS compliance across federal filings',
        'State tax and registration alignment',
        'Sales tax and nexus structuring',
        'Payroll and employment tax compliance',
        'Multi-state reporting consistency',
        'Entity and tax structure alignment',
        'Platform-aligned accounting',
        'US GAAP aligned financial reporting',
        'IRS compliance across federal filings',
        'State tax and registration alignment',
        'Sales tax and nexus structuring',
        'Payroll and employment tax compliance',
        'Multi-state reporting consistency',
        'Entity and tax structure alignment',
        'Platform-aligned accounting',
      ].map(item => (
        <span class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full inline-block" style="background-color: #1a4480;"></span>
          {item}
        </span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== CERTIFICATION BLOCK ===== -->
  <section style="background-color: #060D18; border-bottom: 1px solid #1E293B;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-10">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase" style="color: #334155;">Standards</span>
        {['ISO 27001 Certified', 'IRS and State Aligned', 'US GAAP Reporting', 'Multi-State Compliance Ready'].map(cert => (
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg" style="background-color: #0F172A; border: 1px solid #1E293B;">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" style="color: #1a4480;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"/></svg>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold" style="color: #94A3B8;">{cert}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== WHY AMBIT ===== -->
  <section style="background-color: #0F172A;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-24">
      <div class="mb-14">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4" style="color: #1a4480;">Why Ambit</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black leading-tight max-w-3xl" style="color: #F8FAFC;">
          Why US Businesses Work With Ambit
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base max-w-2xl leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">
          Operating in the United States requires alignment across federal tax, state tax, sales tax, payroll taxes, and financial reporting standards. As businesses grow across jurisdictions, these obligations often become fragmented across systems, filings, and reporting cycles. Ambit brings structure across accounting, tax, payroll, and financial management so that compliance and reporting remain consistent without increasing internal complexity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {[
          {
            title: 'US GAAP Expertise',
            body: 'Financial records and reporting aligned with US accounting standards.',
            icon: 'M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 11h.01M12 11h.01M15 11h.01M4 19h16a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z',
          },
          {
            title: 'Federal and State Awareness',
            body: 'Processes structured across IRS and state-level requirements.',
            icon: 'M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3',
          },
          {
            title: 'Real-Time Financial Visibility',
            body: 'Reporting designed to support decisions, not just compliance.',
            icon: 'M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6',
          },
          {
            title: 'Scalable Support',
            body: 'Capacity expands without creating additional operational burden.',
            icon: 'M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15',
          },
        ].map(({ title, body, icon }) => (
          <div class="rounded-xl p-6" style="background-color: #0D1829; border: 1px solid #1E293B;">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5" style="background-color: #1a4480;">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d={icon}/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold mb-2" style="color: #F8FAFC;">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">{body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== SERVICES ===== -->
  <section id="services" style="background-color: #060D18; border-top: 1px solid #1E293B;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-24">
      <div class="mb-14">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4" style="color: #1a4480;">What We Offer</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black leading-tight" style="color: #F8FAFC;">Finance, Accounting & Tax for US Businesses</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base max-w-2xl" style="color: #64748B;">Each function is structured to ensure consistency across reporting, compliance, and decision-making.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Numbered overview -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-16">
        {[
          { num: '01', title: 'Accounting & Bookkeeping', body: 'US GAAP-aligned records, reconciliations, and reporting across entities and reporting periods.', href: '/services/finance-accounting-tax/us/accounting-bookkeeping' },
          { num: '02', title: 'Tax Compliance', body: 'Federal, state, and multi-state tax compliance structured across registrations, filings, and reporting obligations.', href: '/services/finance-accounting-tax/us/tax-compliance' },
          { num: '03', title: 'Payroll', body: 'Payroll processing and employment tax compliance aligned across federal and state requirements.', href: '/services/finance-accounting-tax/us/payroll' },
          { num: '04', title: 'Financial Management', body: 'Reporting, analysis, planning, and performance visibility across operations.', href: '/services/finance-accounting-tax/us/financial-management' },
          { num: '05', title: 'Business Formation', body: 'Entity setup, registration, and structuring across federal and state jurisdictions.', href: '/services/finance-accounting-tax/us/business-formation' },
        ].map(({ num, title, body, href }) => (
          <a href={href} class="rounded-xl p-6 group block transition-all hover:border-blue-700" style="background-color: #0D1829; border: 1px solid #1E293B;">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-3xl font-black leading-none flex-shrink-0" style="color: #1E293B;">{num}</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-bold mb-2" style="color: #F8FAFC;">{title}</h3>
                <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">{body}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Service cards -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          { title: 'Accounting & Bookkeeping', body: 'Structured accounting, reconciliations, and reporting aligned with US GAAP and operational requirements.', href: '/services/finance-accounting-tax/us/accounting-bookkeeping', icon: 'M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 11h.01M12 11h.01M15 11h.01M4 19h16a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z' },
          { title: 'Tax Compliance', body: 'Federal, state, and multi-state tax compliance managed across filings, registrations, and ongoing obligations.', href: '/services/finance-accounting-tax/us/tax-compliance', icon: 'M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z' },
          { title: 'Payroll', body: 'Payroll processing and employment tax compliance handled accurately across reporting cycles and jurisdictions.', href: '/services/finance-accounting-tax/us/payroll', icon: 'M17 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm7-5a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z' },
          { title: 'Financial Management', body: 'Cash flow visibility, budgeting, forecasting, and performance analysis structured for decision-making.', href: '/services/finance-accounting-tax/us/financial-management', icon: 'M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z' },
          { title: 'Business Formation', body: 'Entity formation, EIN setup, state registration, and structural alignment from the outset.', href: '/services/finance-accounting-tax/us/business-formation', icon: 'M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-2 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4' },
        ].map(({ title, body, href, icon }) => (
          <a href={href} class="rounded-xl p-6 group flex flex-col transition-all hover:border-blue-700" style="background-color: #0D1829; border: 1px solid #1E293B;">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5" style="background-color: #1a4480;">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d={icon}/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold mb-2" style="color: #F8FAFC;">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4 flex-1" style="color: #64748B;">{body}</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: #1a4480;">
              Explore Service
              <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== COMMON CHALLENGES ===== -->
  <section style="background-color: #0F172A; border-top: 1px solid #1E293B;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-24">
      <div class="mb-14">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4" style="color: #1a4480;">Common Challenges</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black leading-tight max-w-2xl" style="color: #F8FAFC;">US Accounting and Tax Challenges</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base max-w-2xl leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">
          US businesses operate across multiple layers of compliance. These challenges typically arise when systems, reporting, and filings are not structured together.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-6 text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #93C5FD;">
          See How We Can Help
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {[
          { challenge: 'Late IRS or state tax filings', solution: 'Structured filing processes ensure federal and state deadlines are managed consistently.' },
          { challenge: 'Payroll and employment tax errors', solution: 'Payroll and employment tax obligations aligned across federal and state requirements.' },
          { challenge: 'Disorganised or inaccurate books', solution: 'Financial records maintained consistently in line with US GAAP.' },
          { challenge: 'Sales tax and nexus confusion', solution: 'State-wise obligations, registrations, and sales tax treatment structured clearly.' },
        ].map(({ challenge, solution }) => (
          <div class="rounded-xl p-6" style="background-color: #0D1829; border: 1px solid #1E293B;">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="color: #374151;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/></svg>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: #F8FAFC;">{challenge}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="color: #1a4480;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">{solution}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== INDUSTRY SPOTLIGHT ===== -->
  <section style="background-color: #060D18; border-top: 1px solid #1E293B;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-24">
      <div class="mb-14">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4" style="color: #1a4480;">Industry Spotlight</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black leading-tight" style="color: #F8FAFC;">Serving a Wide Range of US Industries</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          { title: 'Accounting and Tax Firms', body: 'Structured support across client accounting, reporting, and tax workloads.' },
          { title: 'Startups and Growth Companies', body: 'Foundational reporting and compliance structures aligned from the outset.' },
          { title: 'E-commerce', body: 'Sales tax, multi-channel reconciliation, and reporting across jurisdictions.' },
          { title: 'Real Estate', body: 'Property accounting, entity reporting, and tax alignment across portfolios.' },
          { title: 'Healthcare', body: 'Structured reporting, payroll, and compliance support in regulated environments.' },
          { title: 'Professional Services', body: 'Clear books, reliable reporting, and consistency across engagements.' },
        ].map(({ title, body }) => (
          <div class="rounded-xl p-6" style="background-color: #0D1829; border: 1px solid #1E293B;">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold mb-2" style="color: #F8FAFC;">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">{body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CASE STUDIES ===== -->
  <section style="background-color: #0F172A; border-top: 1px solid #1E293B;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-24">
      <div class="mb-14">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4" style="color: #1a4480;">Case Studies</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black leading-tight" style="color: #F8FAFC;">Operational Impact Across US Businesses</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          { label: 'E-commerce Business', result: 'Improved sales tax alignment and cleaner reporting across multi-state operations.' },
          { label: 'Accounting Firm', result: 'Faster reporting cycles through structured support across recurring workloads.' },
          { label: 'Real Estate Business', result: 'Consistent monthly financial reporting and improved entity-level visibility.' },
        ].map(({ label, result }) => (
          <div class="rounded-xl p-8" style="background-color: #0D1829; border: 1px solid #1E293B;">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4" style="color: #1a4480;">{label}</div>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #94A3B8;">{result}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== TESTIMONIALS ===== -->
  <section style="background-color: #060D18; border-top: 1px solid #1E293B;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-24">
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4" style="color: #1a4480;">Testimonials</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black" style="color: #F8FAFC;">Trusted Across the United States</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl">
        {[
          { quote: 'Ambit brought structure to our reporting and tax processes across multiple states. The difference is consistency.', name: 'CFO', company: 'Multi-State Business, United States' },
          { quote: 'Payroll, filings, and financial reporting are now aligned. There is much more clarity across the business.', name: 'Founder', company: 'Growth Company, United States' },
        ].map(({ quote, name, company }) => (
          <div class="rounded-xl p-8" style="background-color: #0D1829; border: 1px solid #1E293B;">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mb-4" style="color: #1a4480;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: #94A3B8;">{quote}</p>
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs font-bold" style="color: #F8FAFC;">{name}</div>
              <div class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #475569;">{company}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== PROCESS ===== -->
  <section style="background-color: #0F172A; border-top: 1px solid #1E293B;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-24">
      <div class="mb-14">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4" style="color: #1a4480;">Our Process</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black leading-tight" style="color: #F8FAFC;">How Work Is Structured for US Businesses</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base max-w-xl" style="color: #64748B;">A defined five-step process from understanding requirements through ongoing delivery.</p>
      </div>

